{"tid":1033561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"認真講 係F.1女仔最壞係我同凱婷","createTime":"2019-02-23T09:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T11:50:43.000Z","uid":52749,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3950ee3c006056e6405d4c7c01148f39bdfaed0e","tid":1033561,"uid":52749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"知吾知自己好撚戇鳩？<br />\n我都忍左你好撚耐<br />\n日日扮撚哂大家姐<br />\n認真講 係F.1女仔最壞係我同凱婷<br />\n你要扮我地吾會阻止<br />\n哈 點知你越扮越衰<br />\n有啲野我同凱婷都未出聲<br />\n有時連班男既都未出聲啦<br />\n幾時輪到你出聲呀？<br />\n有啲野心照架<br />\n壞學生？你做到咩？<br />\n吸煙飲酒介手就代表壞囉<br />\n你連扣分 係學校搞事都吾敢啦<br />\n點做壞學生呀？ 小姐<br />\n你想學我地咋嘛<br />\n入黑社囉 係學校搞事呀！<br />\n最好學理我負分都要比人繼續扣<br />\n你敢？你連續兩支煙都食吾撚到啦<br />\n學我地？！算把啦 傻系"},{"pid":"89b1d19855ae7c87a3771f726f91fcb84044cacc","tid":1033561,"uid":52749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f94a7e28df55e2e605c202500a3822ed799996d","tid":1033561,"uid":217683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f3bd4b59475b45647d49ecdae2712f797bb6d4","tid":1033561,"uid":226216,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH1LDeR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH1LDeR.gif&h=203d5519&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8db31ae8060d0fd69d4cbcccf559d2132e01190","tid":1033561,"uid":142804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbf33fb81701ce4341186835cbce1f497009762","tid":1033561,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e708523fc4201b3c33604be1aa